verbose_text: Decrease of TGF-beta level in tumor tissue may be the reason of decreased epithelial to mesenchymal transition (EMT) process observed in tumor tissue of mice treated with both compounds combined, as TGF-beta is one of the most important molecules involved in EMT process XREF_BIBR.
evidence: TGF-beta level in tumor tissue may be the reason of decreased epithelial to mesenchymal transition
